title: Aromatherapy and Essential Oils for Beginners
description:
Aromatherapy and Essential Oils for Beginners: Au Naturoil: A Guide for Stress Relief, Healing Remedies and Natural Cleaners - With Over 100 Essential Oil Recipes by Susan Burgess

Overview: Aromatherapy and Essential Oils for Beginners - Discover the Uses of Safe, Natural Ingredients for Aromatherapy and Essential Oils in Everyday Life

Unlike most store-bought products, these do-it-yourself recipes contain no harmful chemicals or preservatives. This book on aromatherapy and essential oils is perfect for beginners and includes over 100 natural recipes for:
Treating Skin Ailments
Treating Aches and Pains
Alleviating Allergy Symptoms
Treating General Health Issues
